## 🔄 Demo Workflow

The example workflow below demonstrates how AgentOps Control Tower governs a high-risk AI agent action.

```text
┌───────────────────┐
│   AI SOC Agent    │
└─────────┬─────────┘
          │
          ▼
┌───────────────────┐
│ Requests Action   │
│ Block IP Address  │
└─────────┬─────────┘
          │
          ▼
┌───────────────────┐
│ Policy Engine     │
│ Approval Required │
└─────────┬─────────┘
          │
          ▼
┌───────────────────┐
│ Approval Queue    │
│ Pending Review    │
└─────────┬─────────┘
          │
          ▼
┌───────────────────┐
│ Human Approval    │
│ Approved          │
└─────────┬─────────┘
          │
          ▼
┌───────────────────┐
│ Action Executed   │
│ Block IP          │
└─────────┬─────────┘
          │
          ▼
┌───────────────────┐
│ Audit Log Created │
└───────────────────┘
```

